dict.string: Thomas helped the Logging Locos to the Sodor Steamworks for repairs. Sir Topham Hatt was excited to see that Thomas was safe—and that with all the jobi wood Thomas had found on Misty Island, the Rescue Center would be finished in no time.

Thomas helped the Logging Locos to the Sodor Steamworks for repairs. The Fat Controller was excited to see that Thomas was safe—and that with all the jobi wood Thomas had found on Misty Island, the Rescue Centre would be finished in no time.
